P:BAX is perfect for:

UL:
LI:Bloggers wanting a simple, SEO-friendly site
LI:Developers who hate installing dependencies
LI:Non-technical users who want to build websites
LI:Students learning about static sites
LI:Documentation site creators
LI:Portfolio websites
LI:Small business landing pages
LI:Anyone who wants a fast, simple website
/UL:

