HR:

H2:What's in a Name?
P:BAX stands for:

UL:
LI:B - Batch (Windows script)
LI:A - Axcora Tech (the creator)
LI:X - Cross-platform excellence
/UL:

P:It's short, memorable, and represents the simplicity we value.

HR:

H2:The Philosophy of BAX
P:BAX is built on these core principles:

H3:Simplicity First
P:Every feature in BAX is designed to be simple and intuitive. No unnecessary complexity.

H3:Zero Dependencies
P:BAX uses only what your operating system already has. No downloads, no installations, no conflicts.

H3:Performance Matters
P:BAX is optimized for speed. Build times are measured in milliseconds, not seconds.

H3:SEO is Essential
P:Good SEO should be automatic, not an afterthought. BAX handles it all.

H3:Cross-platform by Default
P:Your content should work everywhere. BAX runs on Windows, Linux, and macOS.

